init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: a scene of a man in a car, driving through a forest.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man in the car gets out and walks towards the child.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You know, I have been thinking about you a lot lately" Mark says.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "He is in the other room, playing with his guitar" the child says.
